Meowy Christmas from all of us to you 🐱🎄🤍

May your holidays be plump and filled with delicious food or warm cuddles!🎅

Thank you for still being here with us- we appreciate you so much 🫶🤍

📸: Hoodie Maple, Rapper Maple, Lily Loafie, Fluffy Honey, Busy Izzie, and Chonky Loafie

Which portrait is your favorite? Personally can’t get over hoodie Maple LOL. We need to buy more sweaters. 😂

Maple Cat is calling you 👀

Will you pick up? Tag a Maple bestie because we’re back 👋

— 

How have you been? We’ve missed you. 🤍 
Let’s catch up!

Happy 6th birthday to this young potato of a cat 🎂🤍

(Undoubtedly had many treats today but still eats like he’s never had a food in a day of his life)

—

May you live many many healthy years and keep gracing us with these sweet jiggly cheeks. 🥰

There’s no amount of words that can describe how much I love you to the moon and back. We were always fated to be together and I couldn’t be more blessed to be your cat mom.🫰🤍

On the evening of 4.18.23, Honey and Maple welcomed a healthy litter of two boys. 🤍 @cheeky.cats 

The first is a shorthair boy who has a vibrant golden coat, deep emerald eyes, and a playful and demure personality. 🥰

Our second is our first longhair in our cattery with black paws, a hungry stomach, and a rambunctious energy haha. 

It’s honestly been such a sweet journey having a pair again- and Clover (their older sister) has loved raising them like her own. 

Will you help us suggest some names starting with the letter ‘D’ for litter D? ☺️

P.S. stay tuned in our stories for their first time eating solids!

Do you have an unimpressed cat like ours? 😒@Samsung is looking for the best photo to be
featured in their Neo QLED 8K commercial! 🐾 #ad

Good luck! 🤍

I jus a babee 🦁 

—

Almost coming to 3 months old and the boys still prefer nursing on mama Honey, despite eating solids. 😂 I told Honey we should be raising them to be gentlemen but she still loves nurturing them. 

No I haven’t figured out names yet 😂 I just call this on Floof and the other one Not Floof lol. I’m lame. 

Hope you all a flooftastic furriday. 🥰

Tag someone who needs serotonin today 🦁

To all the kittens I've loved before 🤍 happy #nationalkittenday!

-

A day late but still wanted to share some of our cutest photos of the kittens we've come to raise over the years. Photos of @cheeky.cats litter A all the way through D are all here. 🥺

This journey of raising kittens ethically and responsibility has been such a long but joyous one. Each kitten has such a special bond with me raising them from palm-sized to kitten-hood. I've been lucky to share a piece of my heart with the wonderful families they live with and couldn't be happier how much love they bring others. 🤍

The secret to a purrfect fur free home 🤭 @roborockglobal #ad

Did you know that Meowmy has allergies to cats? And despite that, she still has 7 haha… a lot of that is helped by vacuuming daily! But as you can imagine, that’s a lot of work, especially with shedding season.

That’s why the Roborock S8 Pro Ultra is such a game changer to our multi-cat household! Not only does it vacuum, but it also mops. Meowmy never has to pick up another hairball, vacuum dry food crumbs, or wipe up spills. Cleaning can be scheduled through the app and not only is it all automatic, it’s completely self-cleaning as well! 🙏 

With its amazing 3D Obstacle Avoidance System and LiDAR navigation, the Roborock S8 Pro ultra can detect moving pets and avoid important objects, like Meowmy’s harps. ☺️

With so many cats, our S8 Pro Ultra is a holy grail item that helps Meowmy not only breathe easy but also keeps our home fresh, comfortable, and clean. 🤍
